snippet.title: Netherworld: Beyond Time I stand intro
snippet.description:
A hard to find action game for the pc. This was originally made by Irrational Games, the developers who made Bioshock, but was sold and finished by FX Labs.

The game runs poorly for odd reasons, hence the unstable frame-rate. This is only a problem in the first level and is much better for the rest of the game.
